array.note: b[i][j] is 1 if a black queen is in the cell at row i and column j
w[i][j] is 1 if a white queen is in the cell at row i and column j

group.note: no two opponent queens can attack each other

sum.note: ensuring the same numbers of black and white queens

maximize.note: maximizing the number of black queens (and consequently, the size of the armies)
